snippet.title: 8-bit Panda (TIC-80) Gameplay
snippet.description:
8-bit Panda is the most popular game on the TIC-80 fantasy console platform. It was created by btco (aka. Bruno Oliveira).

The player controls a panda character that can collect bamboo and kill enemies, with no boss enemies. This game contains 17 levels, and there are no bonus levels.

I managed to beat the first 2 isles before getting bombarded by the snow enemies from isle 3.

The game can be played here: https://tic.computer/play?cart=188
